---
---
<section id="problema" class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
    <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green">El problema</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance">Un sistema de recoleccion disenado para otra epoca</p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600">Las rutas se planifican con semanas de anticipacion, sin datos reales. Los camiones recorren rutas completas aunque los contenedores esten al 30% de capacidad.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats with left border -->
  <dl class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 text-gray-900 sm:mt-20 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3 border-l border-eco-green/30 pl-6">
      <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">de basura generada al dia en CDMX</dt>
      <dd class="order-first text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">12,700 ton</dd>
      <dd class="text-xs text-gray-400 italic">Fuente: SEDEMA</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3 border-l border-eco-green/30 pl-6">
      <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">invertidos en vehiculos e infraestructura (2025-2026)</dt>
      <dd class="order-first text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">$500 MDP</dd>
      <dd class="text-xs text-gray-400 italic">Fuente: Expansion</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3 border-l border-eco-green/30 pl-6">
      <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">en tiempo real sobre el estado de los contenedores</dt>
      <dd class="order-first text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">0 datos</dd>
      <dd class="text-xs text-gray-400 italic">Fuente: INECC</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>

  <!-- Before/After -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-4xl">
    <p class="text-base/7 text-gray-600 mb-10 text-center">El resultado: costos innecesarios, emisiones evitables, contenedores desbordados y ciudadanos insatisfechos. Mientras el transporte de personas ya se transformo con Uber, Waze y Google Maps, la recoleccion de basura sigue operando con rutas fijas y horarios rigidos.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
      <div class="bg-red-50/60 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Hoy</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-red-400 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22z"/></svg>Rutas fijas y estaticas</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-red-400 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22z"/></svg>Sin informacion de contenedores</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-red-400 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22z"/></svg>Decisiones manuales por intuicion</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-red-400 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22z"/></svg>Impacto ambiental no medido</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50/60 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Con EcoRuta</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Rutas dinamicas en tiempo real</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Datos continuos via IoT</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Decisiones automatizadas con IA</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Reduccion medible de CO2 y combustible</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
